{{IceHockeyAt2014WinterOlympics}}
The '''women's tournament in [[ice hockey at the 2014 Winter Olympics]]''' is currently being held in [[Sochi]], [[Russia]].

==Qualification==
{{main|Ice hockey at the 2014 Winter Olympics <U+2013> Women's qualification}}
Russia qualified as the host. Canada, the United States, Finland, Switzerland, and Sweden qualified as the top five teams in the [[IIHF World Ranking]]. Germany, and Japan qualified via the qualification tournament.<ref name="iihf">{{cite web |url=http://www.iihf.com/home-of-hockey/championships/olympics.html |title=2014 Olympic Winter Games |publisher=IIHF.com |accessdate=10 February 2013}}</ref>

